item.title: Typescript类型定义文件(.d.ts)生成工具
item.description: Microsoft/dts-gen - dts-gen creates starter TypeScript definition files for any module or library. dtsmake - d.ts file generator tool from JavaScript files. dtsgenerator - d.ts file generator tool, for only JSON Schema files. js2tsd - d.ts file generator tool, no type inferrence. JS2TSD d.ts file generator GUI tool app. Not CLI.
